==以電單車作為救護車==
早在[[第一次世界大戰|第一次世界大戰]]期間，英、美、法等參戰國已經因為[[摩托車|電單車]]的輕巧，而開始研究以電單車作為救護車的可行性。<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=cA0LAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA490 Outing: Sport, Adventure, Travel, Fiction] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=cA0LAAAAIAAJ&pg=PA490 |date=20150322152745 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=GdQqAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA101 The Scientific American War Book: The Mechanism and Technique of Warfare] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=GdQqAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA101 |date=20150322131835 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=M61IAAAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA165 Popular Mechanics Magazine:  Written So You Can Understand it] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=M61IAAAAMAAJ&pg=RA1-PA165 |date=20150322133702 }}{{en}}</ref>

[[w:Motorcycle_ambulance|救護電單車]]是一種輔助或獨自進行緊急醫療服務的緊急車輛，一般不運載病患；但在一些地區，會使用拖架或邊車（Side car）運送病人。救護電單車的優勢，是能夠在交通繁忙或道路狹窄的地方，以遠遠超過標準救護車的速度處理緊急醫療個案。目前，全球有多個國家或地區採用救護電單車。

